  <brief_title>VTX-2337 in Combination With Radiotherapy in Patients Low-Grade B-cell Lymphomas</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I/II Study of Intratumoral Injection of the Small Molecule TLR8 Agonist VTX-2337 in Combination With Local Radiation in Low-Grade B-cell Lymphomas</official_title>
